### Phase 7 — Notifications + SLA

@host = http://localhost:8080
@customerToken = paste-customer-token
@agentToken    = paste-agent-token
@adminToken    = paste-admin-token
@notificationId = paste-notification-uuid

### 1. List own notifications
GET {{host}}/api/v1/notifications?page=1&per_page=20
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 2. List ONLY unread (note `meta.unread_total`)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/notifications?unread_only=true
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}

### 3. Mark one notification as read (idempotent)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}

### 4. Try to mark someone else's notification — EXPECTED 404
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 5. Mark all as read
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}

### 6. Dashboard summary (now includes SLA + unread_notifications)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Ticket detail carries the SLA block
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/paste-ticket-id
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}
